title: NFL Draft Fantasy Analysis: Best/Worst Fits for Rookie Wide Receivers and Running Backs (Football 4/30)
description:
The NFL Draft is now in the past, but fantasy drafts are set for the not-too-distant future. Will Brinson is joined by Jamey Eisenberg to break down the class of 2020 from a fantasy perspective. How soon until Joe Burrow, Tua Tagovailoa and Justin Herbert become fantasy relevant? The guys talk QBs and follow up by chatting about the best and worst fits for rookie wide receivers and running backs.
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
